@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dmdbcr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.96)))
    v1 = v2
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.90 / tmp + 0.47) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.36)) * wp.cos((v2 + 0.56 - tmp + 0.49)))
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
